.vs/
.idea/
*.swp
*~

## Local code intelligence index
.codegraph/

## OS
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
.DS_Store
$null

## Fixtures (large / third-party mods — keep samples local)
tests/fixtures/**
!tests/fixtures/.gitkeep
!tests/fixtures/README.md

## Local secrets / game paths
*.key
local.settings.json
.env

## Oodle (keep extracted DLL; ignore zip and extras)
third_party/oodle/*.zip
third_party/oodle/ar/
third_party/oodle/bin/*.pdb
third_party/oodle/bin/ozip.exe
third_party/oodle/bin/oodle-network*

## Reverse-engineering dumps (never commit)
third_party/fet_extract/
third_party/**/decompiled/
tools/

## MMC compile-only refs (copy from your MMC install; not redistributed)
third_party/mmc-refs/*.dll

## Release output
dist/
artifacts/


